race.comment: SO BE INSPIRED (6) just found one better at Ipswich last time out when well in the betting and will be ready to peak now fourth run back from a break. Has placed two of three over this sprint journey and must be respected from the Lees barn. Looks very hard to toss. STARSARISE (4) was a touch disappointing at the latest effort but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance with the 3kg claim. I AM VOODOO (1) saves his best form for this course and distance with six wins and nine placings from 20 starts. Has to be included in calculations. FAST FUSION (2) is a two-time winner over this track and trip and is another to get some weight relief. In the mix. NIRVANA THE STORM (5) strips fitter second-up and may trouble the judge.
